    "description": "Manufactured OpenAPI artifact for BigCommerce APIs. This file was synthesized by Last Mile from curated research JSON and is not vendor-certified. Use it as an agent-consumable starting point, then validate paths, schemas, authentication, and server URLs with the vendor before production use. BigCommerce's public API overview describes several public API families: REST Store Management APIs, REST Storefront API, GraphQL Storefront API, Customer Login API, Current Customer API, GraphQL Admin API, GraphQL Account API, and Payments API. The public examples explicitly cover adding and updating products, changing order status, creating coupons, managing customer accounts, updating billing addresses at checkout, clearing carts, querying products and categories, authenticating storefront customers, and integrating with SSO providers. This is a write-capable ecommerce platform, but it does not represent asset or telemetry data. Asset data is Unsupported. Telemetry data is Unsupported. Writeback is Supported.",
